(68883, 165605, 0, 1, 'It Becomes Me', '', '2013-01-01 00:00:00', 2000, 20, 1, 1, 'We are the same kind of people\nWe turn lies into realities\nLiving in it with complete comforts\nDying in it with only numbness\n\nWithout heart I perform these deeds\nDeeds would hurt badly through your spirit\nForget the guilt, I feel no shame\nForget the guilt, I feel nothing\nThere is something...\n\nSomething, there''s something haunted like\nthickened air, breath in, breath out. There is\nSomething, there''s something sinking down\nto nowhere, nowhere to be found\nIt becomes me\nOh it becomes me\n\nWe are the same kind of people\nWe run in to the circle with no ending\nMake the same mistakes again and again\nBreak the hearts that would never mend\nLooking back on the days down the trace\nThe trace leads me to only darkness of regrets\nForgive the guilt, I feel the shame\nForgive the guilt, I feel everything\nThere is something...\n\nSomething, there''s something haunted like\nthickened air, breath in, breath out. There is\nSomething, there''s something sinking down\nto nowhere, nowhere to be found\nIt becomes me, becomes me\n\nNo pain, no pain\nMore lies, no pain\nNo pain, no pain\nMore lies, no pain\nNo pain, no pain\nMore lies, no pain\n\nSomething, there''s something haunted like\nthickened air, breath in, breath out. There is\nSomething, there''s something sinking down\nto nowhere, nowhere to be found\nSomething, there''s something haunted like\nthickened air, breath it in, breath it out. There is\nSomething, there''s something sinking down\nto nowhere, to be found\nIt becomes me\n\n【中譯】\n我們都是同一種人\n把謊言變成真實\n安逸活著\n麻木死去\n\n無所用心行動著\n卻狠狠傷透靈魂\n遺忘了罪疚 我感覺不到羞愧\n遺忘了罪疚 什麼都感覺不到\n有些東西\n\n縈繞著 像\n愈加厚重的空氣 呼吸著 有些東西\n正往下沉落\n沉得無處可循\n而它漸漸成為了我\n成為了我\n\n我們都是同一種人\n無止境循環著\n犯著相同的過錯\n傷了無法癒合的心\n回頭看著以往的日子\n卻只看見沉重的後悔\n原諒了罪疚 我感覺到羞愧\n原諒了罪疚 我感覺到一切\n\n不會痛苦 不會痛苦\n更多謊言 就不會痛苦', '', 295, '', '樂冰/本能State of the Heart', '羅西', '含書/本能State of the Heart', '本能 State of the Heart', '', 1, 1, 0, '2013-12-04 05:20:45'